1/4. {{champion:7}} 
{{champion:107}} kept his new empowered W and new W healing, he kept his new passive “hunting each champion” interaction, he still has 4 stacks instead of five, his stacks still fall off when out of combat unlike before, and his Ult still has eyes on whoever he’s closest to unlike before. All that’s been reverted is the Q and some ultimate numbers. 
So don’t go sayin he’s been completely reverted.
